================================================================
 Stupa Server : an Associative Search Engine
 (http://code.google.com/p/stupa)

 Copyright(C) Mizuki Fujisawa <fujisawa@bayon.cc>
================================================================

Overview:
  This software is a server implementation of Stupa,
  an associative search engine.

Build:
  * Build all
    % make

Usage:
  * Start stupa search server
    % stupa_evhttpd [options]
       -p port     port number (default:147258)
       -d num      maximum number of documents (default: no limit)
       -i size     maximum size of inverted indexes (default:100)
       -w nworker  number of worker thread (default:4)
       -f file     load a file (binary format)
       -h          show help message

Requirement
  * C++ compiler with STL (Standard Template Library)
  * Stupa C++ library
  * libevent <http://www.monkey.org/~provos/libevent/>

